data.description: Motivated Seller!! The seller is willing to contribute $10,000.00 in closing cost! This 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath is an absolute dream. The home has been well maintained over the years and has so much to offer! The home is over 5,000 square feet between the 2 floors, the unfinished basement, and the finished attic space that has been converted to a fourth bedroom and a bonus room. The entry way to the home is warm and inviting. The natural light in the home gives a beautiful glow while you look out at the gorgeous trees. The kitchen offers a large amount of storage and counter space. Enjoy the large walk-in closet in the master along with the soaking tub in the master bathroom. The unfinished basement allows you to expand the home to whatever your heart desires. The newly added pergola at the back of the home adds a great space to entertain or just to enjoy a quiet evening outdoors. The back yard is fenced in to keep your fur babies safe and sound. This home has had so much love put into it and every detail has been carefully thought out.  The floors on the main floor are LVP and the carpet in the home is stain and pet resistant. While living in this beautiful home, you are a part of the Fairfield Plantation community which adds a sense of security and entertainment. It is a gated community that takes pride in keeping their families safe. Whether you like eating a dinner while looking over the water, hitting the beach area, swimming, or going golfing, there is something to do for most everyone without leaving the comforts of your own community. Don't miss this home!
